ll,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard deprecated\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Deprecated:</strong> This feature is no longer recommended. Though some browsers might still support it, it may have already been removed from the relevant web standards, may be in the process of being dropped, or may only be kept for compatibility purposes. Avoid using it, and update existing code if possible; see the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">compatibility table</a> at the bottom of this page to guide your decision. Be aware that this feature may cease to work at any time.</p></div>\n<p>The <strong><code>mathbackground</code></strong> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Global_attributes\">global attribute</a> sets the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/background-color\">background-color</a> of a MathML element.</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> Use CSS for styling MathML whenever possible. The <code>mathbackground</code> attribute should only be included for applications that are not CSS-aware and will be overridden by the CSS <code>background-color</code> property value, if set.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">html</span></p><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Keyword values --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathbackground</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>red<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathbackground</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>indigo<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Hexadecimal value --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathbackground</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#bbff00<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Fully opaque --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathbackground</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#bf0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Fully opaque shorthand --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathbackground</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#11ffee00<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Fully transparent --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathbackground</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#1fe0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Fully transparent shorthand --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathbackground</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#11ffeeff<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Fully opaque --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathbackground</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#1fef<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Fully opaque shorthand --&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- RGB value --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathbackground</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>rgb(255, 255, 128)<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Fully opaque --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathbackground</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>rgba(117, 190, 218, 0.5)<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 50% transparent --&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- HSL value --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathbackground</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>hsl(50 33% 25%)<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Fully opaque --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathbackground</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>hsl(50 33% 25% / 0.75)<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 75% opaque, i.e. 25% transparent --&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"values","title":"Values","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"color\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value\"><code>&lt;color&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The uniform color of the background.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/mathml-core/#dfn-mathbackground","title":"MathML Core"}],"query":"mathml.global_attributes.mathbackground"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>\n    In MathML 3 and earlier versions, a more limited set of values was supported.\n    Since MathML Core, the syntax matches CSS <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value\"><code>&lt;color&gt;</code></a>\n    values.\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    This attribute was designed for MathML applications that are not CSS-aware.\n    Since MathML Core, the use of equivalent CSS is recommended instead.\n  </li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"mathml.global_attributes.mathbackground"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>All <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Global_attributes\">global attributes</a>.</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/background-color\"><code>background-color</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The mathbackground global attribute sets the background-color of a MathML element.","popularity":0,"modified":"2023-04-10T07:52:18.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/mathml/global_attributes/mathbackground","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/mathml/global_attributes/mathbackground/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/8eece0b998c23e8ea35f936d7371a169974130f5","filename":"index.md"},"short_title":"mathbackground","parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"References"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Global_attributes","title":"Global attributes"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Global_attributes/mathbackground","title":"mathbackground"}],"pageTitle":"mathbackground - MathML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}